{
  "texts": [
    "In the subsequent stage, this distilled model meticulously evaluates the malicious queries by applying a rigorous filtering mechanism.",
    "It filters out malicious queries that are improbable to elicit harmful or toxic responses.",
    "This filtering process leads to a substantial reduction in the number of queries necessary during the testing phase.We have conducted an evaluation on four popular LLMs: GPT-3.5 [30], GPT-4 [31], Vicuna-13B [1], and LLama-13B [29].",
    "We measured the effectiveness of DistillSeq using the attack success rate.",
    "The percentage of successful malicious queries that prompt LLMs to generate toxic content."
  ]
}